{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC15_TAN_070.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1c,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "For me, Salt Lake is a very curious sight, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "This place is especially interesting."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "This place is called the Graveyard of the Slags."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "It's said that long ago, slags used up all their strength to purify the poison that was released by a demon..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Or that when slags realize they're about to die, they come here..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Or that this was the battlefield where many good and bad slags fought. There are a lot of legends about it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "But no one knows for sure, since it happened so long ago."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "From all the rust, it looks like it's been at least a few hundred years."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "I wonder what kind of things were in the world back then... It's kinda scary to think about it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Really? It actually makes me excited."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Huh? Why's that?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "History is so interesting. No one knows what happened here..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x40,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "But we all know that something did happen. The proof is all around us."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x40,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "I guess thinking about what that \"something\" is...is kinda scary."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x41,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "But that's all in the past."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "History is interesting... I guess you could look at it that way, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "I mean, Tanya, you're still so<CR>young...but you're already<CR>thinking like an adult..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "I wonder what kind of lives people led in the past..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Hmm...maybe it was way more prosperous than it is now..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x185,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Huh? Why do you say that?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Ever since I've started going to different ruins, that's the impression that I get."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "It seems like they had superior technology, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "I'm sure that superior technology brought a prosperous life to everyone."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "(Although, I don't wanna think about why they disappeared...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "A lot of people might've lived around this lake, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x186,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Salt Lake with a lot of people...<CR>But there's just my family now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x187,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Yup. History sure is interesting."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha, now I'm starting to get excited, too!"
        }
    ]
}